    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project or daily driver for someone comfortable with a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof panels. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all essential electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely require some suspension work and a fresh set of tires in the near future to bring it back to peak performance.",
