    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly immaculate condition. This specimen has been meticulously preserved, maintaining its original showroom luster and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that exceeds expectations. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
